औr Ek to sIzan jIjI BऐyA Ek to sIzan BI cal rahA hऐ nA Ap is bAt ko BI to samJiE mAMg zyAdA hऐ Ek to sIzan BI sIzan hऐ to is wajah Am kA rEट थoDA sA mahaMgA cal rahA hऐ औr kElE kI aBI kElA BI BAI bilkul sAfsuथrA Ap खud dEखEq kitnE kitnE sAfsuथrE kElE raखE hऐq औr Am BI Ek to sIzan cal rahA hऐ is wajah sE थoDA sA rEट tEz A rahA hऐ hamArE ko खud jo maqडI hऐ wahAM sE yahI rEट mil rahA hऐ hamEq ham to खud kam lAgat sE matlab 
