Pir agar sar 
डऑkyUmEqट sar AधAr kArड pऐn kArड ApkA rAशan kArड औr sar janm pramAण patr jahAM rahtE hऐq wahAM jAti niwAs yahI sab औr घar kI prऑparटI jo jissE sar agar Ap lon nahIq dE pAE to ham logoq kA prUP rahE gAnA sar kI yE wo 
